# Student Grade Prediction ðŸŽ“

Predict student performance (pass/fail + grade tendency) from academic and study-related features using a simple, end-to-end machine learning pipeline.

## Overview

This project uses a synthetic dataset of student records (attendance, internal marks, assignments, study hours) to train and evaluate classification models. It demonstrates a realistic workflow: data generation â†’ preprocessing â†’ model training â†’ evaluation â†’ single-record prediction.

## Features

- Synthetic dataset generator script
- Clean tabular ML pipeline
- Models:
  - Logistic Regression
  - Random Forest Classifier
- Evaluation with precision, recall, F1-score
- JSON-based prediction script to infer pass/fail for a single student

## Tech Stack

- Python
- NumPy, Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- Joblib

